author: Chris Tomlinson
title: Sweden: Three Injured in Shooting and Stabbing Attack
text: Swedish policemen patrol on December 13, 2010 near the Drottninggatan shopping street in Central Stockholm, where an apparent car bomb and a separate blast targeted Christmas shoppers two days ago. Sweden's chief prosecutor said today investigators were almost certain the author of the failed suicide attack was Swedish citizen Taymour Abdel Wahab. AFP PHOTO / JONATHAN NACKSTRAND
